<dl>
    <dt>Ensure the device is not suspended</dt>
    <dt>Ensure all messages are marked as read in the messages indicator</dt>
    <dt>From a supplementary device, send a text message to the SUT</dt>
        <dd>Incoming SMS shall be notified on screen</dd>
        <dd>If the calling number is in the addressbook and if the number isn't hidden by the operator, the name of the originator shall be displayed; if not, the phone number when not hidden by the operator</dd>
        <dd>The messages indicator shall turn blue</dd>
    <dt>Pull down the messages indicator</dt>
        <dd>The recieved message shall be seen from the indicator</dd>
    <dt>Open the phone application</dt>
        <dd>The recieved message shall be seen from the indicator</dd>
</dl>
<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
